AddFaq(8, "Who wrote this bulletin board?", "This software (in its unmodified form) is produced, released and is copyrighted by [email=peter.goodman@gmail.com]k4[/email]. It is made available under the [url=http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php]MIT license[/url] and may be freely distributed; see link for more details", $db);
AddFaq(8, "Why isn't X feature available?", "This software was written by and licensed through k4. If you believe a feature needs to be added then please visit the official k4 website and see what the k4 Group has to say. Please do not post feature requests on any of our boards, as we use sourceforge to handle tasking of new features. Please read through the forums and see what, if any, our position may already be for features and then follow the procedure given there.", $db);
